  "title": "Households by Main Source of Lighting Fuel",
  "type": "multi-block",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "The Nepal Electricity Authority (NEA) has been implementing plans for electricity maintenance, revenue collection, and electrification in all wards of this Sub-Metropolitan City. According to the National Census, 2021 (BS 2078), electricity appears to be the primary source of fuel used for lighting daily."
